summary: You know Buffy Driscoll? That amazingly strong girl, determinated, self-confident, not-scared of anything challenging, the...
body:
You know Buffy Driscoll? That amazingly strong girl, determinated, self-confident, not-scared of anything challenging, the friend that we all want, the one who has your back at any time, cares for you more than anything, can be extremely annoying yet you couldn’t live without her, makes mistakes but is able to recognise and be sorry for them (kinda), is so so beautiful, has and amazing sense of style, supported her friend when he came out to her and had the best reaction everyone should have? Do you know her?



Yeah, I love that girl.

summary: would anyone be interested if i like.... gave away some of my fan art?  not the most time-consuming pieces i’ve done, but little...
body:
would anyone be interested if i like…. gave away some of my fan art? 

not the most time-consuming pieces i’ve done, but little sketches and stuff?? maybe mail them out with short little notes to you???

because i am feeling CLUTTERED with so many little loose papers hanging around, in addition to all the sketchbooks i’ve filled up (oh, to be a traditional artist….)

i don’t want to just trash the physical copies, so…. maybe…. is this a thing worth doing??

summary: tbh tyrus would be that one couple who were lucky enough to find each other early in life and end up being everyone’s favorite...
body: tbh tyrus would be that one couple who were lucky enough to find each other early in life and end up being everyone’s favorite sweethearts because theyd push through all the odds and experience all phases of life together while not suffering from toxicity within their relationship. This doesn’t mean theyll always be happy together of course, they’ll fight, they’ll have rough patches but all in all I could see them as having one of the most healthy relationships u can have and I think that’s beautiful.
